<p align="left"><b>ABSTRACT</b></p>
<p>An AI Code Generator Chatbot is an intelligent assistant designed to help developers write code faster. It uses Artificial Intelligence to understand user requirements in natural language and generates appropriate programming code. It significantly reduces development time, helps beginners learn programming by providing ready-to-use examples, and assists skilled developers in finding quick solutions to complex problems and writing repetitive boilerplate code.</p>

<p>The primary objective of this project is to build an interactive chatbot interface for instant code generation. It aims to provide accurate, functional, and optimized code snippets based on user prompts while supporting multiple programming languages and frameworks. Additionally, the system includes memory capabilities so the chatbot remembers the context of the ongoing conversation, and offers advanced input options like speech-to-text and file analysis.</p>

